data.description: Are you in need of a 5-bedroom home with 3.5 Baths?  Well, here it is.  Wonderful curb appeal, exceptional stonework & color coordination, as well as outstanding garage doors. Walk into this inviting home, with a large formal living room on the right, and a formal dining room.   The kitchen is a cook's dream with a flat top range, double oven, double bowl sink, an awesome island, super large pantry, and plenty of room for a table. Kitchen & family room are an open floor plan, large gas fireplace, sliding doors to the outside oasis.  Beautiful, heated swimming pool, hot tub, hard scaping, fire pit, and lots of outdoor furniture, which is negotiable, a vacation spot in your own home.  Upstairs, are 4 spacious bedrooms, all carpeted, all new overhead lights with fans, and all with California Walk in Closets.  A full bath, for 3 bedrooms.  Primary suite is spacious, a sitting area, jacuzzi tub, stand up shower, and double bowl vanity, as well as a large walk in California Closet.   All TVs are professionally hard wired and will stay with the home.  The lower level is unbelievable, a large custom bar with marble, a media room, the 5th bedroom, an exercise area, and another full bath. Great spot to entertain or watch a movie with the family.  Keyless entry and a security system.  Absolutely a fabulous home!  Call me today for a private showing.  Contingent on the seller finding suitable housing.
